(1, '63', 'Start TeeSpring Campaigns', '17/05/2020', '17/05/2020', 'teespring.jpg', '\r\n<p>What is TeeSpring.com?\r\n\r\n<p>Teespring is the best way to design and\r\nsell customized clothing online. You\r\ndesign a product and sell it. The sales\r\nmoney pays for the production of your\r\ndesign and we send it to all your buyers.\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Artists, designers, painters.\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Ability to conceive and create designs.\r\n<p>-Ability to convert designs into digital\r\nformat using tools such as Photoshop.\r\n<p>-Ability to promote your designs on social\r\nmedia\r\n\r\n<p><b>Time needed to start a TeeSpring\r\ncampaign:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>When your design is ready, you can\r\ncreate a teespring campaign in minutes.\r\n\r\n<p><b>Generating revenue:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Select the color and size of the T-shirt.\r\nUpload the design.\r\n\r\n<p>-Start promoting your T-shirt on\r\nsocial media and /or using paid\r\nadvertisements.\r\n\r\n<p>-More T-shirts that you sell, more\r\nmoney you earn.\r\n', 'Keywords for teespring', '27', '1', '1', 'description for teesrping', ''),
(2, '63', 'Sell Arts and Crafts on Etsy', '17/05/2020', '', 'etsy.jpg', '<p>What is Etsy.com?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Etsy is an online buyers and sellers\r\ncommunity similar to eBay, but focuses\r\non selling art, handmade or vintage items\r\nand supplies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With around 30 million visitors per\r\nmonth, Etsy offers a wonderful platform\r\nfor craftsmen, designers and creative\r\ndesigners to help them spread their work\r\nto the global audience and grow their\r\nbusiness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your goal should be to use Etsy\'s\r\npowerful visitor base to reach millions\r\nof people and sell your products to them\r\nwithout getting into trouble creating your\r\nown website, promoting it and handling\r\npayment processing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Etsy\'s top sellers earn a maximum of S\r\n1 million a year by selling art, handicraft\r\nand handcrafted items.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you take action, you can also be one of\r\nthem.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Artistic and Creative people who like\r\nto design, design and Create their own\r\nitems/ products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Creative skills to imagine, conceive,\r\ndesign and create things that can be sold\r\nonline.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ability to promote your Etsy store\r\nusing social media channels such as\r\nFacebook, Instagram and Twitter, along\r\nwith other methods such as blogging,\r\nguest posting, networking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Time needed to create your store on\r\nEtsy:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can log in almost immediately on\r\nEtsy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But while creating your store you\r\nhave to create its title, get pictures\r\nof items you want to sell, write a\r\nconvincing description, determine price\r\ndetermination points.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To complete the above steps, it can take\r\none or two days.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Tips:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Determine what you are going to sell-\r\nBefore you put your feet in Etsy, make a\r\nlist of items that you think you can make.\r\nOnce the list is ready, go to Etsy and type\r\nin keywords to find other sellers offering\r\nsimilar items you want to sell.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Discover what they sell? how do their\r\nproducts differ from others? What are\r\ntheir pricing strategies?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do some competitive analysis and try to\r\nfind items in your list that experience less\r\ncompetition.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Based on your initial research and\r\ncompetition analysis, create an item that\r\nyou think is more suitable for creating\r\nyour initial space on Etsy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Select a name for your store - Once you\r\nregister an account with Etsy, you must\r\nfirst set up your store. And naming your\r\nstore is the first step of the installation\r\nprocess.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Select a name that represents what\r\nyou want to sell. But do not waste time\r\nsearching for a perfect name.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Etsy gives you another chance to rename\r\nyour store, so choose a name right away\r\nand think about it later.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Set up your store - Here are the\r\nimportant steps you need to follow when\r\nsetting up the store.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Create a logo</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Creating a logo is very important for\r\nbuilding a brand and improving credibility.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Make sure that the logo you design is\r\nunique and represents the items you\r\nwant to sell.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you do not have graphic design skills, it\r\nis always better to outsource the design\r\ntask of a logo to someone on Fiverr.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tell them what you want and let Fiverr\r\nexperts do the work for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Take attractive item photos</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Photos become the first point of contact\r\nbetween your potential customer and\r\nyour item.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You must therefore ensure that your\r\nphotos do the work to attract the\r\nattention of the customer and convince\r\nhim/her to read the description.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If they do not find the photos of an\r\nitem attractive, they will never read the\r\ndescription of your item.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A trick is to study the photos of other\r\nsuccessful stores that sell similar\r\nitems like yours and then replicate their\r\ntechnique.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If possible, try to take photos with\r\na digital SLR camera and use white\r\nbackgrounds.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Offer varying prices and sizes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most of the successful Etsy sellers offer\r\ndifferent article sizes and prices, helping\r\nthem attract all levels of buyers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This strategy helps them to ensure that\r\nthere is always something for everyone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For e.g. If you sell smaller original items\r\nat a lower price, people who can not buy\r\nlarge expensive items can still buy from\r\nyou.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This way you can meet the needs of both\r\nexpensive and budget buyers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Write a convincing description - The\r\ndescription of your article is the second\r\nmost important factor after photos, it is\r\nthe job to convince potential customers\r\nto place an order with you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So make sure you write the most\r\nappealing article description.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The best way to start is to study what\r\nyour competitors have written in\r\ntheir description, to study the biggest\r\nquestions your potential customer is\r\nasking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Take notes and model your description\r\nbased on your notes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also try to answer the questions of\r\npotential customers, so they do not have\r\nreservations when placing an order with\r\nyou.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also communicate important details\r\nabout your item, such as dimensions,\r\nmaterial used, care to be taken during\r\nuse, and so on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Add the right tags and keywords: most\r\npotential customers will find your store\r\nthrough search.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You must therefore ensure that your\r\ntitle and description contain the right\r\nkeywords.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to generate a list of keywords,\r\nthink about what your potential customer\r\nwould type into the search bar to find\r\nwhat you are selling.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sniff the title and description of your\r\ncompetitor to dig up more relevant\r\nkeywords.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also create a list of relevant keywords\r\nthat appear in the automatically-proposed\r\nlist of the Etsy search bar and add them\r\nto your listings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Other options for Etsy:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you plan to sell arts and crafts, Etsy\r\nshould be your first choice of platform.\r\nBut if you want to expand your reach even\r\nfurther, you can consider selling your art\r\non the following websites.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is the list of optional sites for Etsy:</p>\r\n<br>Zibbet.com\r\n<br>HandmadeArtists.com\r\n<br>UncommonGoods.com\r\n\r\n<p>AftCra.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SuperMarketHQcom</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HyenaCart.oom</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Generating revenue:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Generating income is very simple. More\r\npeople place orders with you, more\r\nmoney you earn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your customer\'s assessment will have\r\na major impact on improving your sales,\r\nbrand building and credibility.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So make sure you deliver quality items\r\nwithin your promised delivery dates.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Take the time and care during the\r\npackaging of your item so that it does not\r\nbend, break or break during transport.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Try to cover the costs of packaging\r\nmaterials in your shipping costs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That\'s all!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Have fun with selling arts and crafts on\r\nEtsy.</p>\r\n', 'keywords', '0', '1', '1', 'description', ''),
(3, '63', 'Do CPA Marketing', '17/05/2020', '17/05/2019', 'cpa-marketing.jpg', '<p>What is CPA?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPA stands for \'Cost Per Action\'</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPA is one of the most popular ways\r\nto make money on the internet. CPA\r\nmarketing is very simple: you get paid\r\nwhen someone clicks your afflliate link\r\nand completes an action.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That action could be:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Providing an e-mail address</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sign up for a free trial of a product</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Download a mobile app</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Request a quote</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPA is simpler because you earn money\r\neven if a product is not sold.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unlike afflliate marketing, where\r\nsomeone has to buy a product to receive\r\ncommissions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPA model works for lead generation.\r\nMany large companies are willing to\r\npay large commissions for generating\r\ntargeted leads.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your job is to give them only a head\r\nstart, they will do the rest of the work to\r\ngenerate a sale of those leads.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-People who like to talk, write, explain and\r\nhave the ability to convince.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Best for people who already have a blog\r\nor website with daily traffic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Ability to promote links to CPA partners\r\nusing social media, videos, forums\r\nmarketing, paid advertising, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Ability to convince and convince\r\npeople through proper arguments and\r\nexplanations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Time needed to start CPA Marketing:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to start CPA marketing and\r\nearn commissions, you need to find an\r\noffer to promote and then be accepted by\r\na CPA network.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can find an offer almost immediately,\r\nbut it can take up to a week before you\r\nare accepted for a CPA network.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But once accepted, you can immediately\r\nstart promoting an offer of your wish.\r\n<p><b>Tips:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Find different offers - Your first step\r\nhere will be to find different CPA offers\r\navailable on the market.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And the best way to find them out is to\r\nvisit oDigger.com and CfferVault.com.\r\nBoth sites work as search engines for\r\nfinding CPA offers. They collect offers\r\nfrom all reputed CPA networks available\r\nworldwide.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Select your perfect offer- If you already\r\nhave a blog in a particular niche, select\r\nan offer that is related to that niche.\r\nMake sure it is relevant to your blog and\r\naudience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For e.g. If your blog talks about Android\r\napp gaming, then a CPA offer that you pay\r\nwhen someone installs an Android game\r\napp is perfect for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Getting Acceptance - Believe or not, but\r\nbeing accepted in CPA networks has\r\nbecome a huge stumbling block for most\r\nmarketers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most CPA networks now implement strict\r\ncontrols to ensure that only high-quality\r\nand legitimate marketers can access\r\ntheir offers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is to prevent fraud or illegal\r\nactivities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are some tips that will help you get\r\nin:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Be honest: CPA networks filter out\r\nscammers and not the legitimate people.\r\nSo make sure that the information you\r\nprovide is genuine and not obscure. Do\r\nnot try to mislead them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Know your offer- lf you already know\r\nwhat offer you want to promote, then it\'s\r\na great plus. You will be asked for when\r\nyou Complete the application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This shows that you are one with a plan.\r\n\r\n<p>Know your traffic sources - when filling\r\nin your application you will be asked for\r\nyour traffic sources. You must therefore\r\nknow how people will reach your offer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Are you going to promote it via e-mail\r\nmarketing, mobile ads, writing an article\r\non a blog or something else, then you\r\nhave to tell clearly about it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Optimize your blog - Once you\'ve joined a\r\nnetwork and selected your CPA offer, it\'s\r\ntime to promote it on your blog. The best\r\nway to do this is to integrate your affiliate\r\nlinks into the content of the blog.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is the best way to get higher click\r\nspeeds. Another way is to place banners\r\nin the header or sidebar section.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Always do some experiments and try to\r\noptimize your link placement to maximize\r\nyour click-through percentages, but make\r\nsure you damage the user experience of\r\nyour blog.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Generating revenue:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Provisions for CPA offers typically range\r\nfrom S 0.10 to S 10 per promotion. In\r\nsome niches, such as insurance, lawyers\r\nand antivirus software, it can go up to S\r\n50 per action.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imagine if you could get 10 people to\r\ndownload a trial version of an antivirus\r\nsoftware that pays you S 50 per\r\ninstallation, you\'ll earn S 500 without even\r\nselling anything.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The commissions offered are determined\r\non the basis of factors such as niche,\r\nproduct costs of the back-end, product\r\ndemand and supply, target country and so\r\non.\r\n\r\n<p>In order to earn maximum commissions,\r\nit is best to choose offers that are\r\nrelevant to your target group and pay\r\nhigher commissions.</p>\r\n', 'keywords for cpa marketing', '1', '1', '1', 'description for cpa marketing', ''),
(4, '63', 'Amazon Associates', '17/05/2020', '17/05/2019', 'amazon-associates.jpg', '<p>What is the Amazon Associates\r\nprogram?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Amazon Associates is an afflliate\r\nmarketing program that allows website\r\nowners and bloggers to create links and\r\nreferral commissions when a visitor\r\nclicks through the website and buys\r\nproducts from Amazon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-People who like to write, explain things in\r\ndetail and want to share their knowledge\r\nand expertise with the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Best for people who already have a blog\r\nor website with daily trafflc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-The opportunity to express knowledge in\r\nwriting in a simple but effective way.\r\n<p>-Ability to convince and convince\r\npeople through proper arguments and\r\nexplanations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Time needed for becoming an Amazon\r\npartner:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To become an Amazon Associate, all\r\nyou have to do is visit their website and\r\nsign up. You must enter the name of your\r\nwebsite when signing up.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Amazon will analyze your website and if\r\nthey find it appropriate according to their\r\nstandards, they will approve you as an\r\nofficial Amazon partner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The approval process can take 2 to 5\r\ndays.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once you\'ve been approved, find the\r\nrelevant products you want to promote\r\non your blog, then grab their affiliate links\r\nand add them to your website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Tips:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-lnvolve relevant products - The first and\r\nmost important thing is to find out which\r\nproducts are relevant to the content and\r\nthe public of your website or blog.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The more relevant the product, the more\r\nchance you have to sell.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For e.g. Promoting wrist watches on\r\na blog that teaches people to do yoga\r\nexercises is unlikely to make any sales.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But instead, if you try to promote yoga\r\nmats, pants and books, you will see great\r\nsuccess.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Place linked links in your content-\r\nPlacing simple text links within the\r\ncontext of an article is the most effective\r\nway to let people click on your afflliated\r\nlinks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>People rely more on the content of a\r\npage than on another part of the website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Therefore, it is very likely that they\r\nclick on the link when it is placed in the\r\ncontents of the content.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For e.g. \"View this cool [your aff link]\r\nsmartwatch [/ your aff-link] and has kept\r\nthe position of number 1 bestseller since\r\nthe last two months.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Link product images to Amazon - Images\r\nplay an important role in attracting\r\nvisitors\' attention.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The other easy way to get people to click\r\non your affiliate links is to use many\r\nhigh-quality product images and make\r\nthese images as clickable affiliate links.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A good thing about Amazon is that\r\nit allows you to freely use the image\r\nof every product on your website for\r\npromotional purposes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Write an article about product reviews doing a quality review and writing a\r\ngood article that explains all facets of a product is a great way to generate high click rates and sales.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But while you conduct an assessment,\r\nyou must ensure that it is of high quality\r\nand unbiased.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>People should not think that you are\r\ntrying to let them buy the product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A high quality assessment must answer\r\nall answers and clear confusion or\r\nconcerns that potential buyers have.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Make sure your assessment covers all\r\nthe above aspects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Just send people to Amazon - One of\r\nthe great things about Amazon is that\r\nit is very good at converting visitors to\r\nbuyers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You do not have to follow them and do\r\nnot target them with ads, Amazon does\r\nthe rest for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All you have to do is send them to\r\nAmazon.com through your affiliate link.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The great thing about this is when\r\nsomeone visits Amazon.com through\r\nyour link, you get a percentage of\r\neverything they buy for the next 24 hours\r\n(30 days after they have added an item to\r\ntheir shopping cart).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For e.g. lf one person clicks on your\r\n\"Yoga l\\/lat\" link and visits Amazon.com\r\nand buys 2 wrist watches within 24\r\nhours instead of a yoga mat, you will\r\nreceive commissions for the sale of wrist\r\nwatches, even if you have not promoted it\r\ndirectly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Build loyalty and trust- An important\r\nfactor that will stimulate your sales is the\r\nloyalty and trust of your reader towards\r\nyou and your website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most of your sales will be people who are\r\nloyal and repeat readers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Readers who contact you on a regular\r\nbasis begin to trust you and your website\r\nover the long term.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So when you make a recommendation or\r\ncarry out an assessment, they take that\r\nadvice rather than someone they do not\r\ntrust.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Generating revenue:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The monetization formula is similar to\r\nmost other methods discussed in this\r\napp.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>More people visit Amazoncom through\r\nyour affiliate link and buy products, more\r\nmoney you earn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Amazon.com will handle all payment and\r\ncommission payments for you so you do\r\nnot have to worry about it.</p>\r\n\r\n', 'keywords for amazon associates', '1', '1', '1', 'description for amazon associates', ''),
(5, '63', 'Teach Your Native Language', '17/05/2020', '17/05/2020', 'teach-language.jpg', '\r\n\r\n<p>Most people in today\'s globalization\r\nworld are trying to learn new languages,\r\nand there are many new reasons for\r\ndoing so.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some people want to improve their\r\nemployability, others want to study or live\r\nabroad, some want to grow their business\r\nor just want to improve their travel\r\nexpenence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The point is, there is a huge market of\r\nonline language learners who are willing\r\nto pay for language coaching.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your goal must be to make use of this\r\nopportunity, to learn the language you\r\nknow online and to make good money.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But how are you going to find the people\r\nwho sign up for your language coaching?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The simple answer to this question is to\r\nregister on iTalki.com.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What is iTalki.com?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>iTalki is a popular online platform for\r\nlanguage learning that connects people\r\nwho are willing to learn languages to\r\nothers who can teach them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With 2 million students and 3,000\r\nteachers teaching the world\'s 100\r\nmost important languages, this is the\r\nlargest marketplace for online language\r\nteachers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>People who like to teach and have a gift\r\nto transfer knowledge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-In oral and written fluency in a speciflc\r\nlanguage you wish to teach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-A clear understanding of the learning\r\nprocess of the language.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-The possibility to give the training step\r\nby step.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>To work:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To begin, go to iTalki.com and submit an\r\napplication to become an online teacher.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once approved, you can create your\r\nteacher proflle, set up your online\r\nschedule, create your language courses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hereafter, you will be listed on iTalki\r\nlists and prospective students from\r\naround the world can view your proflle\r\nand decide that the</p>y will book you for an\r\nonline session.\r\n\r\n<p>All iTalki sessions are performed online\r\nvia Skype and other VOIP software. So\r\nmake sure you have a super fast internet\r\nconnection and suitable headphones.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The main advantage of iTalki is that\r\nit handles everything for the teacher:\r\nmarketing, planning, payment and student\r\nmanagement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a teacher you only have to teach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Tips:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-As a teacher at iTalki you will face\r\ncompetition from other teachers on the market.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So you have to make sure that you have a\r\nstrong teacher profile that distinguishes\r\nyou from others.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Students will make the decision to\r\nchoose you as a teacher on the basis of\r\nthe following criteria, so make sure you\r\nhave optimized them all.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Prices\r\n<p>As a new teacher you have to offer your\r\neducation at the beginning at a very\r\ncompetitive price.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Start with a small price, as soon as you\r\nget more students and have collected\r\nhigh ratings, you can raise the price later.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Profile</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Believe it or not, your profile photo will\r\nhave a huge impact on attracting your\r\npotential students to your profile, since\r\nyour profile photo is the first thing they\r\never see on offer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Take a professional photo in good setup\r\nand in light conditions, wear formal\r\nclothing if possible, not only cut an\r\nordinary photo with your mobile phone\r\ncamera and upload it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Video introduction</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Will you set up your teacher profile,\r\nthen you will be asked to post a video\r\nintroduction.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is your best chance to bring your\r\nlanguage skills to the attention of your\r\npotential students.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Shot a 3-4 minute professional-looking\r\nvideo that explains to students about\r\nyour approach to teaching, syllabus and\r\nother teaching methods that are unique\r\nto you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The purpose of the video introduction is\r\nto convince potential students that you\r\nare an expert in the language and have\r\nthe right didactic skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p>lf you already have some experience\r\nwith online language teaching, have\r\nCompleted advanced courses or have\r\na university degree, show them in your\r\nprofile to increase your chances of being\r\nselected.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Reviews and feedbacks</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These will have the greatest impact\r\non your potential student\'s decision to\r\nchoose you for another teacher or not.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Make sure you offer the best possible\r\ncourse and help students learn the\r\nlanguage quickly and effectively.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Expected income:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you teach, you earn lTCs (iTalki\r\ncredits) that you can withdraw for real\r\nmoney with PayPal, Alipay, Webmoney,\r\nMoneybookers (Skrill).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10 lTCs are equal to $1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most language teachers charge between\r\n100 lTCs and 200 lTCs (S 10 to S 20) per\r\nhour, depending on their expertise and\r\nfeedback.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also run language tests, add\r\ncall preparation modules, child modules,\r\neto. to diversify your market reach and\r\nincrease income.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So the formula for making money here\r\nis simple, more students report more\r\nmoney that you earn on your course.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>\r\n\r\n', 'keywords for teach-language', '8', '1', '1', 'description for teach-language', ''),
(6, '63', 'Do Interview Transcribing', '17/05/2020', '17/05/2020', 'transcribing.jpg', '\r\n<p>What is an interview that is being\r\ntranscribed?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Transcription means to make a\r\nwritten copy of something. Interview\r\ntranscription is listening to an audio or\r\nvideo interview and converting it into a\r\nwritten copy for reading purposes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nowadays, most journalists, non-fiction\r\nwriters and bloggers conduct thousands\r\nof hours of interviews and most of them\r\nare too busy to transcribe themselves.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So they outsource this task to speed up\r\nthe publication process. That is where\r\nthey need interview transcribers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your job as a call receiver is to listen to\r\nthe audio or video interview and write it\r\ndown word for word.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Almost everyone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-More suitable for people to love writing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-The language of your operation can read,\r\nwrite and speak fluently.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Possibility to listen and understand\r\nmultiple accents in your language of\r\noperation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-The ability to type faster is a must.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>To work:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The first way is to register on the\r\nfollowing transcription services sites and\r\ncomplete the available tasks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is the list:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Verbalink.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Scribie.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The second way is to contact local\r\nnewspapers, magazines and TV news\r\nchannels to see if they can offer you a\r\ntranscription job.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The third way is to contact bloggers,\r\nnews site owners and non-fiction writers.\r\nVisit their sites, search their e-mail and ask if they need a\r\ntranscriber.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Expected income:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You earn $5 to $40 per hour for\r\ntranscribing an interview, depending on\r\nyour expertise.</p>', 'Keywords for transcribing', '1', '1', '1', 'description for transcribing', ''),
(7, '63', 'Do Documentation Translation', '17/05/2020', '17/05/2020', 'translation.jpg', '\r\n<p>What does a document translator do?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When Companies grow globally, they\r\nhave to communicate with their clients\r\nin a language that their customer\r\nunderstands.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most companies communicate in writing\r\nwith their customers, such as e-mail,\r\nmanuals for product use, help tutorials,\r\nwritten blog content, and so on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To do this, they need people who are\r\nmultilingual and who can effectively\r\nconvert a document written in one\r\nlanguage into another language.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a document translator, your job is to\r\nconvert documents written in a language\r\ninto another language.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The most common example you should\r\nhave seen is a guide to the use of\r\ntelephones that you receive when you\r\nbuy a new phone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You should have noticed that this guide\r\nhas multiple versions written in multiple\r\nlanguages.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This job is done by document translators.\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Almost everyone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-More suitable for people who like to\r\nwrite.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Ability to read and speak fluently at least 2 or more languages.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Ability to interpret the meaning of the context with correct understanding.</p>\r\n<p><b>Tips:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Set up your home office with a computer,\r\ninternet connection, a recording\r\nheadphone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You need this when you decide to\r\nparticipate in live conversations and\r\nconvert documents online.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Most translation assignments are in\r\nSpanish, Japanese, Korean, Chinese and\r\nFrench.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So try to learn and be fluent in one of\r\nthem. These will give you more money.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>To work:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The best way to get started is to upload\r\nyour CV and mention your rates and\r\nservices on Translatorscafe.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It contains a free online guide with\r\ntranslators and translation assignments.\r\nAnother way is to register yourself at the\r\nfollowing top websites; these sites offer\r\ntranslation assignments based on your\r\nexpertise and skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is the list:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gengo.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lingosaur.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Expected income:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You earn about $12 / hour for translating\r\nnormal documents and up to $40 / hour\r\nfor translating technical or scientific\r\ncontent.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'keywords for translation', '0', '1', '1', 'description for translation', ''),
(8, '63', 'Start Your Prodcast', '17/05/2020', '', 'podcast.jpg', '<p>What is a podcast?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A digital audio flle available on the\r\ninternet for download to a computer or\r\nportable media player, usually available\r\nas a series, new parts of which can be\r\nreceived automatically by subscribers.</p>\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>People who like to talk and explain\r\nthings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Thorough knowledge of every subject in\r\nwhich you are interested.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Possibility to convince with logical\r\nreasoning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Time needed to create a podcast:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are 3 important steps for creating a\r\npodcast</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Prepare a script. Determine what the\r\ncontent will be. Make an overview to\r\nkeep track of what you are going to\r\ndiscuss or promote.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Record audio for your podcast.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Upload your podcast to your personal\r\niTunes website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Generating revenue:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Sell your podcast. But make sure the\r\ncontent of the podcast is convincing to\r\npersuade people to pay for it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Add a commercial to your podcast and\r\nearn money.</p>\r\n', 'keywords for podcast', '', '1', '1', 'description for podcast', ''),
(9, '63', 'Develop a software', '17/05/2020', '', 'software-development.jpg', '<p>I will not advise you to choose this way,\r\nbecause it can take a lot of time to read\r\na good number of books and then give\r\nreviews.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Generating revenue:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Become an Amazon partner. Promote\r\nbooks on your website using your\r\namazon affiliate links.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you use your ratings, you convince\r\npeople to buy books through your\r\naffiliated links.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>More people will buy books from your\r\naffiliate link more money you earn.</p>\r\n\r\n', 'keywords for software-development', '', '1', '1', 'description for software-development', ''),
(10, '63', 'Become an Online Tutor', '17/05/2020', '', 'online-teacher.jpg', '<p>Due to the growth of a busy lifestyle,\r\nmany people today prefer the\r\nconvenience of online coaching.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The growth of technology and internet\r\nhas made the experience of online\r\ncoaching extremely realistic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a result, the demand for online\r\nteachers is growing rapidly. So if you like\r\nto help others learn, online tutoring can\r\nbe the earning ticket for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>People who like to teach and have a gift\r\nto transfer knowledge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Expertise in a specific subject that you\r\nwant to teach, such as math, science,\r\ncomputer programming and so on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-A college education or at least two years\r\ncompleted study in the subject that you\r\nwish to teach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Some experience as an online tutor is an\r\nadvantage, but not necessary.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>To work:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The first and the best way is to sign up\r\nat the online tutoring sites, these sites\r\nwill assign your students based on your\r\nproflle and planning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The following is the list of reputed online\r\ntutoring sites:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tutor.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TutorVista.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>e-Tutor.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SmarThinking.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The second way is to start alone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Create a local advertisement or flyer with\r\nyour log-in details and contact details and\r\nplace them in libraries, supermarkets and\r\non bulletin boards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ask your friends and relatives to spread\r\nthe word.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Create a Facebook page about your\r\nonline tutoring lesson and invite your\r\nonline friends and acquaintances to find\r\nthem fun and fun online.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Expected income:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You earn $9 to $40 per hour, depending\r\non your reputation and experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are a certified teacher with\r\nexpertise like advanced mathematics,\r\nexact sciences, statistics and computer\r\nprogramming, you can count more than $50 per hour.</p>\r\n', 'keywords for online-teacher', '', '1', '1', 'Description for online-teacher', ''),
(11, '63', 'Start a Book Review Site', '17/05/2019', '17/05/2019', 'book-review.jpg', '\r\n<p>What is a book review site?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As the name suggests, a website for\r\nbook reviews is a website where reviews\r\nabout the books are published.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>People who have the passion to read\r\nbooks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The ability to give a profound, honest and\r\nversatile review of a book.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Time needed to start the book review\r\nWebsite:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can start a website within a few\r\nhours. In this case, making a website is\r\nnot a big challenge, but offering honest\r\nand appealing reviews.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you\'ve read a lot of books since your\r\nchildhood, it\'s not hard to give reviews\r\nabout a good number of books.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But if you\'re just starting to read books,\r\nl will not advise you to choose this way,\r\nbecause it can take a lot of time to read\r\na good number of books and then give\r\nreviews.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Generating revenue:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Become an Amazon partner. Promote\r\nbooks on your website using your\r\namazon affiliate links.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you use your ratings, you convince\r\npeople to buy books through your\r\naffiliated links.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>More people will buy books from your\r\naffiliate link more money you earn.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'keywords for Start a Book Review Site', '', '1', '1', 'description for Start a Book Review Site', ''),
(12, '63', '1-Start a YouTube Channel', '20/06/2020', '', 'start-a-youtube-channel.jpg', '<p>Starting a YouTube channel is the easiest way to make money online and does not require any investment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>YouTube receives almost 5 billion videoo views per day, which proves its strength on the internet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Felix Kjellberg, the owner of PewDiePie (a YouTube account), earned $ 12 million in 2015 with one YouTube channel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You too can see such success if you respond to the opportunity that YouTube offers us at the moment.</p>\r\n\r\n<b><p>Suitable for:</p></b>\r\n<p>People who like to make videos, like to talk to a camera, record documentaries or short films.</p>\r\n\r\n<b><p>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n<p>Possibility to make a video using software tools or record a video with your mobile phone or camcorder.</p>\r\n\r\n<b><p>Time needed to start a YouTube channel:</b></p>\r\n<p>Almost you can start within a few minutes. You must visit YouTube.com, create a channel and upload videos.</p>\r\n\r\n<b><p>Tips:</b></p>\r\n<p>Create a YouTube channel around a specific theme, such as Humor, Tutorial, Recipe, etc. Do not just drop out any random channel with unrelated videos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For e.g. If you like gadgets, you can create a channel with gadget ratings where you can post review videos of the latest gadgets and help people decide if it\'s a right choice for them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Select a theme in which you are really interested. Analyze other videos related to your topic, see how many views these videos get.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It will help you to get an overview of how many people are interested in your theme.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-In general, the views are more advantageous for the theme. As more people search for it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Check if there is a missing concept in the videos that are currently available with regard to your theme.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can use these concepts in your videos to get more views.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Give your best to get in touch with your audience. Review comments that people leave in your videos, learn the hidden expectations your audience has of you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Try to find out what they like about your videos and what they do not. Research which videos get the highest retention rate and look for the reasons behind them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Spit on your competitors and try to model the things that work for them. But never try to copy them, always retain your individuality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Always try to improvise every new video from the previous one.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So if you watch your flrst videos after a few years, you should think aww how bad I was before.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That is a good sign; it shows that you have improved.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Experiment, experiment and experiment. Never afraid to try something new and see how it works.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Experiments are the only way to flnd new and exciting things that can increase your lead on your competitors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Finally, try to Collaborate with other YouTubers who do the same work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Learn their strategies and mindset. Working together can do wonders for yourchannel</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Have fun. Do the things you love and enjoy your life.</p>\r\n\r\n<b><p>Generating revenue:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The general rule for generating revenue on YouTube is very simple. More views for your videos, more money you earn. You simply need to enable the monetization option in your YouTube channel settings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>lt\'s very simple.</p>\r\n', 'youtube channel, youtube, start youtube cannel, business idea', '16', '1', '1', '', ''),
(13, '63', '2-Start Blogging', '22/06/2020', '', 'blogging.jpg', '<p>Being a blogger is one of the easiest ways to make money at home.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unlike any other task, if you blog from home. You do not have to work 9-5.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can easily work at any time of the day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But be careful with blogging, it takes time before it starts earning money for you. So l suggest you jump slowly into this fleld.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>lf you have a day job, do not stop. Start part-time with your blog.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once it is about where it gives you more than your Comfortable limits, it is best to Change to full-time blog mode.</p>\r\n\r\n<b><p>Suitable for:</p></b>\r\n\r\n<p>People who like to write and share their knowledge and expertise with the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<b><p>Required skills:</p></b>\r\n\r\n<p>The opportunity to express knowledge in a simple but effective way in writing. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Time needed to start a blog:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The time required depends on your expertise if you are an expert and you can easily start a blog within a few hours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For a complete beginner a day or two is enough to be ready with the basic conflguration.</p>\r\n\r\n<b><p>Tips:</p></b>\r\n\r\n<p>-Start a blog about something you are really good at.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For e.g. If you like traveling and have traveled a lot, start a travel blog.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Always try to limit your blog to a certain domain. Do not post content across multiple domains in a single blog.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For e.g. Writing about recipe tips on a fashion blog.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Keep your blog speciflc for one domain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Try to create a very unique and phenomenal content with your experience and expertise.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Try to give a lot of value to your readers. Write about something that will make a difference in the life of your reader.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Listen to the readers of your blog. Try to solve the problems they are facing. Always respond to their comments. Let them feel better.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Be committed to your blog. A blog is like a relationship. Give it some love and it will flourish. Ignore it and it will die a death.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>lt makes no sense to be half-hearted in your blog activities - if you do not care, why would anyone else?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Think of content, style, tone of voice, audience, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Look at the people who are already doing what you plan to do. Ask yourself the following questions:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1-How will l stand out among the crowd?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What can l say that has not been said\r\nyet?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2-What is my unique selling point?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3-Why do l want to do this?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Be professional in the way you handle\r\nand grow your blog.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do not criticize other brands, bloggers\r\nor people. Remember what goes around\r\ncomes around.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You do not want something that you said\r\nto come back and bite you one day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Be open-minded and willing to work with\r\nother creative people. You meet some\r\namazing and awe-inspiring people.</p>\r\n\r\n<b><p>Generating revenue:</p></b>\r\n\r\n<p>You can monetize your blog by\r\nrecommending products or services\r\nrelated to the topic of your blog by writing\r\nan informative article or placing banner\r\nads on the relevant pages of your blog</p>.\r\n\r\n<p>You can earn handsome commissions\r\nwhen someone buys a product you have\r\nrecommended.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Another way is to place Google Adsense\r\nads on your blog. More people click on\r\nyour ads to earn more money.\r\n</p>', 'blogging, start blog', '17', '1', '1', '', ''),
(14, '63', '3-Do Affiliate marketing', '23/06/2020', '', 'affiliate-marketing.jpg', '<p><b>What is affiliate marketing?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Affiliate marketing is a kind of\r\nperformance-based marketing where a\r\ncompany rewards a certain percentage\r\nof the commission for each product\r\npurchased by the customers who have\r\nbeen marketed by the company\'s own\r\nmarketing efforts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>People who like to talk, write, explain and\r\nhave the ability to convince.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ability to promote online products using\r\nsocial media, videos, advertisements etc.\r\n<p><b>Time needed for starting affiliate\r\nmarketing:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Almost within an hour. All you have to\r\ndo is select an online product to pay a\r\ncommission when you promote and sell\r\nit through your affiliate link.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Tips:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Select an online product from the\r\ndomain you are familiar with. For\r\nexample, if you are a dietitian, select a\r\nproduct related to a diet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are many products available in\r\neach domain, you only need to flnd a\r\ndomain that is suitable for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Places to flnd products: Clickbank.com,\r\nShareasalecom, Jvzoo.com. These\r\nwebsites have thousands of products\r\nfrom different domains.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Choose a product that pays at least 50%\r\ncommission for each sale.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Most product websites handle the\r\ngeneric link generation and payouts, so\r\nyou do not have to worry about how you\r\nget your commissions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Just get your custom afflliate link created\r\nby the supplier and start promoting it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-If you want to make direct money with\r\nafflliate marketing, try promoting your\r\nafflliate link on social sites such as\r\nFacebook, Twitter, Digg, StumbleUpon\r\nand Reddit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Generating revenue:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Generating revenue is easy, just make\r\nmore people to buy the product through\r\nyour affiliate link.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Create a Facebook page or Banner ads\r\nwith the goal of promoting the product.\r\nTell people how the product will help\r\nthem to solve their problems.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Improve people\'s knowledge about the\r\ndomain and help them solve other related\r\nproblems.</p>', 'Earn Money Online, Affiliate marketing, marketing, affiliate', '105', '1', '1', 'Earn Money online by doing Affiliate Marketing', ''),
(15, '63', '4-Create Niche Website', '24/06/2020', '', 'niche-website.jpg', '<p><b>What is Niche Website?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Niche Website is a small website aimed\r\nat a specific topic that shares all relevant\r\ninformation on the subject that is both\r\nuseful and interesting for the target\r\ngroup.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A niche website can contain a few pages\r\nor even hundreds of pages, depending on\r\nthe size of the niche.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-People who are interested in a very\r\nspecific topic within a large domain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For e.g. In a large area such as Yoga you\r\ncan choose a specific subdomain, such\r\nas \'Yoga to lose weight\'.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-People who like to talk, write, explain and\r\nhave the ability to convince.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-The ability to create a Niche website\r\nbased on a speciflc subdomain using\r\nWordpress, Blogger or other available\r\nsoftware and tools.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Possibility to promote a niche website\r\nusing social media, advertisements, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Time needed to start a niche website:</b></p>\r\nYou can start a niche website within a\r\nday. But making good content for the\r\nwebsite can take some time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Tips:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Write down as many niche site ideas\r\nas possible, using the subdomain that\r\ninterests you the most.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>-Limit your niche idea based on finding\r\nthe answers to the following questions:</b></p>\r\nWhat is the target size of your niche?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What is the target size of your niche?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ls your audience known for spending\r\nmoney on the purchase of the niche\r\nprojects?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Are there multiple products available that\r\nyou view on your site?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Are there partner programs that generate\r\nmore than 50% commissions?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What is your investment budget?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Create at least 10 articles with rich\r\ncontent that contain 1000 words, those\r\narticles offer great value for your specific\r\ntarget audience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Register for at least 2 affiliate programs\r\nthat offer products related to your niche\r\nwith more than 50% commissions.</p>\r\n<p>-Perform keyword research and search\r\nfor at least 15-20 niche-relevant search\r\nterms and try to rank your site for them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Try to network with the owners of the\r\nauthority blogs in your niche and f|nd\r\nopportunities for guest blogs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Generating revenue:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Promote the products that are relevant to\r\nthe topic of your niche website by placing\r\naff|liate links in the content and sidebar\r\nofyoursHe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Try to attract more visitors to your site\r\nthrough SEO, forum marketing, social\r\nmedia and paid advertising.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>More people visit your niche site and buy\r\nproducts through your affiliate link, more\r\nmoney you earn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How about creating 10 other niche\r\nwebsites with each site that generates</p>\r\n\r\n<p>$500 per month in an afflliated\r\ncommission that would be $5,000 in\r\npassive income per month.</p>', 'niche website, how to make niche website, niche website topics', '', '1', '1', 'Proper Guide for creating a niche website. Full tutorial free', '');
