(16, '63', 'Publish a Kindle eBook', '01/07/20', '', 'kindle-ebook.jpg', '<p>Publishing a Kindle eBook is another easy\r\nway to generate a consistent passive\r\nincome.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Did you know that Amazon.com is the\r\nbiggest competitor of Google than any\r\nother search engine such as Yahoo or\r\nBing?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>More customers try to search a product\r\non Amazon than on a traditional search\r\nengine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When people want in-depth information\r\nabout a specific topic, they do not search\r\nfor blog posts on Google, but instead try\r\nto find a highly recommended book on\r\nAmazon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your goal should be to leverage the\r\npower of the growing reach and\r\npopularity of Amazon.com to generate a\r\nstable passive revenue source.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>People who have in-depth knowledge\r\nabout a particular subject or like to do\r\nresearch and explain it in an easy to\r\nunderstand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-The ability to give detailed insights about\r\na particular subject.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Possibility to give some extraordinary\r\ntips for solving problems of people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Time needed to create an eBook:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The time required is completely\r\ndependent on the creator of the eBook.\r\nWhich topics does he/ she want to deal\r\nwith? How many details does the maker\r\nwant to add?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These are the important factors that\r\ndetermine the time required.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Tips:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Research, research and research. It is\r\nthe key to a successful Kindle eBook\r\nproduct.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Research into what people are looking\r\nfor in the domain related to the subject of\r\nyour eBook.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For example, if you create an eBook on\r\n\"Yoga exercises to lose weight,\" look at\r\nhow many people are looking for yoga\r\nexercises to lose weight on the Internet\r\nand Amazon? What are their expectations\r\nfor a book?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can easily perform this research\r\nby studying the comments, ratings\r\nand popularity of Amazons existing\r\ncompetitors books.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Write for one reader. If you know your\r\nideal reader, you know how much he/she already knows.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can avoid getting bored with obvious\r\ninformation, and you can give exactly the\r\ninformation that he/ she is looking for.</p>\r\n<p>-View how many people ask questions\r\nabout the topic you have chosen using\r\nwebsites such as Quora, Yahoo Answers\r\nand Wiki answers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>More questions mean that more people\r\nare looking for answers and that is a\r\ngood sign.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Watch the holes in the market in your\r\nselected domain. And see if there is a\r\ndemand for a certain topic, see if your\r\neBook can meet that demand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Go to Amazon.com and see how many\r\nbooks are present in your selected\r\ndomain. Buying people who book?</p>\r\n<p>This will help you to understand the\r\ndemand and purchasing power of the\r\nmarket in your domain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Find a few friendly readers that match\r\nyour ideal reader profile and give them\r\nyour first version.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not only will they help to make your\r\nbook better, it will also increase your\r\nconfidence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Generating revenue:</b><p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sign up for Kindle Direct Publishing\r\nProgram, giving exclusive distribution\r\nrights for your Kindle eBook to Amazon.\r\nThis allows you to sell your eBook in\r\nall countries where Amazon.com is\r\navailable, giving it a huge exposure at the\r\nlaunch.<p>\r\n\r\n<p>Create a small niche site about the\r\nrelated topic and promote your eBook\r\nthrough it. The more eBooks you sell, the\r\nmore money you earn.<p>', 'kindle eBook', '', '1', '1', 'Description  for kindle eBook', ''),
(17, '63', 'Create a Membership Website', '02/07/2020', '', 'membership-website.jpg', '\r\n<p><b>What is a membership site?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A membership site is a private website,\r\nwith exclusive Content that is only\r\navailable to registered members.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It usually offers members the opportunity\r\nto be in contact with each other. They\r\npay a monthly fee to be a member of the\r\nwebsite.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>People who like to communicate, guide\r\nand lead with a community.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Thorough knowledge of a certain\r\ndomain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Ability to explore new things and\r\ncontinually generate new and useful\r\ncontent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Time needed to create a membership\r\npage:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This depends on the domain expertise of\r\nthe maker.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Search Google for the Matthew\r\nWoodward tutorial on how to create a\r\nmembership site for free.<p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Tips:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-In the beginning, keep the fee for\r\nparticipating in the membership site\r\nridiculously low.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Try to make a minimally feasible product\r\ninstead of making a perfect product. You\r\ncan always improve your site in later\r\nstages.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-If you have never been part of a\r\nmembership site so far, consider joining\r\nsome of your domains. Study those\r\nsites.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Are you looking for what works well for\r\nyou and other members of that site?\r\nWhat makes it worth the monthly costs\r\nand how could you replicate this?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Communicate and engage in\r\nconversation with members. Your\r\nmembership site should not be the one\r\nthat only infiltrates the content, with little\r\nor no input from the owner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You must provide insider access for your\r\nmembers who want to communicate with\r\nyou.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even if you are busy, you should spend at\r\nleast half an hour a day to get involved in\r\nyour membership site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can do this in different ways, such as\r\nyou can communicate with the members,\r\nanswer their questions or even interact\r\nwith the forum.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Perform group events and challenges\r\nto increase members, engagement with\r\nyoursne.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Organize events, challenges or similar\r\nevents on a regular basis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Make it easy for members to participate.\r\nOffer prizes, show scoreboards or\r\nsomething similar, create a great\r\nincentive for members to participate and\r\nparticipate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Evaluate regularly what works and what\r\ndoes not work. Try to adjust the site\r\naccording to the needs of the member.\r\nFor e.g. If you offer the bulk of your\r\ncontent in text format, but your members\r\nare more engaged with the video content,\r\nyou switch from text-to-video content.</p>\r\n<p>-Try to introduce new initiatives and see\r\nhow your audience reacts to this. Like\r\nlive Q & A calls or the like.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But beware, do not overwhelm members\r\nwith different initiatives at the same time.\r\nIntroduce one thing at a time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Generating revenue:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Generating income is very simple. More\r\nmembers report more income to your\r\nwebsite that you generate from the\r\nmonthly costs that members pay.</p>\r\n\r\n', 'Tags to Create a Membership Website', '', '1', '1', 'Description  to Create a Membership Website', ''),
(18, '63', 'Sell Website On Flippa', '06/07/2020', '', 'flippa.jpg', '<p><b>What is Flippa.com?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Flippa.com is an online marketplace for\r\nselling and buying websites.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b><p>\r\n\r\n<p>People who like to develop websites.</p>\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thorough knowledge of the WordPress\r\nplatform and the creation of websites.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Time needed for creating a website:</p>\r\n<p>Depending on the expertise of the\r\ndeveloper when creating websites.</p>\r\n<p><b>Tips:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Choose a topic that you are passionate\r\nabout. You have to be passionate about\r\nthe subject your website is targeting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you start a website about something\r\nyou do not care about, you will quickly\r\nlose interest and will inevitably start\r\nworking on it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Consider your long-term business model.\r\nTo make your website successful, you\r\nmust do a lot of research beforehand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Try to find the answers to the following questions:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Who are your direct competitors?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How do your competitors earn money?</p>\r\n<p>How will your website earn money?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How can you distinguish your website\r\nfrom others?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How long does it take to make money\r\nwith your website?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Choose a domain name that is relevant\r\nto your topic and appeal to your target\r\ngroup.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A good domain name is an essential part\r\nof branding your blog. Choose .com as\r\nyour domain extension because it looks\r\nmore professional.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Choose a reliable paid host such as\r\nHostgator, Bluehost or whoever suits\r\nyou.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-You must ensure that the design\r\nand layout of your website looks\r\nprofessional.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Believe it or not, but the flrst time that\r\nvisitors make a judgment about your\r\nwebsite within 10 seconds after loading,\r\nmake sure that the design of your\r\nwebsite appeals to them and they like it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Generating revenue:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Register your website on flippa.com.\r\nFlippa works on a bid model, the highest\r\nbidder gets ownership of the website.</p>\r\n<p>-Set the bid price of your website 15\r\ntimes higher than the current monthly\r\nincome of your site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For e.g. If your site earns $500 per\r\nmonth, you can set your site\'s default\r\nselling price to at least $7500.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Start the auction and wait for bids.\r\nPeople are going to bid for buying your\r\nsite.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once you\'ve received the bid that meets\r\nyour target sales price, complete the deal\r\nwith the bidder.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Flippa.com manages all payment\r\nand other technical matters for you and\r\nyou receive your commissions via the\r\npayment method you have chosen.</p>\r\n', 'keywords Sell Website On Flippa', '', '1', '1', 'Description for Sell Website On Flippa', ''),
(19, '63', 'Sell a Video Course on Udemy', '14/07/2020', '', 'udemy.jpg', '<p>What is Udemy.com?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Udemy is an online learning marketplace.\r\nIt has a huge collection of courses in\r\neverything from programming to yoga\r\nand photography and much more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can create a course in text, audio and\r\nvideo formats. Each course is available\r\non request and students can learn at their\r\nown pace, on their own time and on any\r\ndevice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>People who like to teach, explain and\r\nsolve problems.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Thorough knowledge of every domain of\r\nyour choice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Ability to express knowledge in an easily\r\nunderstandable form.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Ability to create and record high-quality\r\nvideos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Time needed to make a video course:\r\nDepending on the size of the course, the\r\nnumber of modules and the time required\r\nfor the preparation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Tips:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Select a topic in which you are\r\nspecialized.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Study the courses that are relevant to\r\nyour topic and see how many people are\r\ninterested and who are actually enrolled\r\nfor the courses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This gives you an overall insight into the\r\npeople who are interested in your subject\r\nand are willing to invest in your course.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Study the other available courses and\r\ndiscover the things you can offer that will\r\nmake your course much better, different\r\nfrom other available courses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Identify your target audience level and\r\nthen create the course content.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For e.g. You must first decide whether\r\nyour course is for a beginners level or an\r\nexpert level of experts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Then, accordingly, you must create your\r\ncourse content that appeals to the right\r\naudience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Make sure that the title and description\r\nof your course is optimized to appeal to\r\nyour target group</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Try answering the frequently asked\r\nquestions your audience asks in your\r\ncourse description.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Deliver at least 80% of your course in\r\nvideo format, because this is the most\r\nexciting way of interaction.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also keep the length of each video lesson\r\nbetween 2-10 minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Build up a relationship with the public\r\nand engage yourself. You can always do\r\na quiz session between lectures to make\r\nit interesting and interactive.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Generating revenue:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Udemy gets a lot of daily visitors, so\r\nthere is a good chance that your course\r\nwill be noticed and that people register\r\nand that you will make money.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-You can even start a small blog about\r\nyour course related topics and promote\r\nyour course.<p>\r\n\r\n<p>-More people sign up for your course\r\nmore money that you earn.</p>', 'sell video course on udemy', '', '1', '1', 'description of udemy course', ''),
(20, '63', 'Sell a Service on Fiverr', '14/07/2020', '', 'fiverr.jpg', '<p>What is Fiverr.com?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fiverr is a global online marketplace\r\nthat offers tasks, services and products,\r\nstarting at a cost of $5.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fiverr receives almost 4.7 million visits\r\nper month.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your goal should be to use the powerful\r\nvisitor base of Fiverr to reach more\r\npeople and sell your services or products\r\nto them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every service or task that you offer\r\non Fiverr is called a GIG. With Fiverr\'s\r\nmillions of visitors, you do not have to\r\nworry about the promotion and payment\r\nhandling of your performance while Fiverr\r\nhandles it for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All you have to do is concentrate on\r\ndelivering high-quality work to keep\r\nyour ratings, since ratings from your\r\ncustomers have a huge impact on the\r\nfailure or success of your performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>People offer a wide range of services\r\non Fiverr, ranging from graphic design\r\nand design, digital marketing, music and\r\naudio, advertising to everything you can\r\nthink of practically.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remember that you can sell your\r\nperformance for any price, S 5 is just the\r\nminimum starting price.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Top Fiverr gig sellers earn more than S\r\n50,000 a year by using the platform and\r\ndelivering high quality services.</p>\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-People who like to help others by making\r\ntheir lives easier.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-People who enjoy the freedom to work\r\ndo what they really like.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>People with profound skills in a specific\r\narea, with whom they can help other\r\npeople to complete their tasks or make\r\ntheir lives easier.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Time needed to create a Gig on Fiverr:</b></p>\r\n<p>You can make a gig on Fiverr for almost\r\nan hour. All you have to do is register with\r\nFiverr first.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>During the performance of a performance\r\nyou must insert the title of your\r\nperformance, upload the image of the\r\nconcert, write a description of the concert\r\nand insert relevant tags and keywords.</p>\r\n<p><b>Tips:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Find your best skills - The first thing you\r\nneed to do is sit quietly and find out\r\nwhich skills you are strongest and stick\r\nto tasks that are related to it until you see\r\nany success.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For e.g. If you are a person who can\r\ndesign logos and websites, you must\r\ncreate and sell those appearances in\r\nFiverr that are aimed at creating logos\r\nand designing websites.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Make your first homework - Before you\r\ndive when making a gig, you need to\r\ndo some research to ensure that the\r\nperformance you want to offer has\r\ninterested buyers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What if you have a great idea, but have\r\nnot sold it?\r\n\r\n<p>To avoid such a situation, you must do\r\nthe necessary research to understand\r\nwhat buyers are looking for in your niche.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Find popular performances related to\r\nyour skills - One of the best ways to see\r\nsuccess with Fiverr is to dig up popular\r\nperformances related to your skills, study\r\nthem, and then model your performance\r\naccordingly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The most important statistics you\r\nhave to look at when studying other\r\nperformances are:\r\n<br>\r\n-Title\r\n<br>\r\n-Description\r\n<br>\r\n-Statue\r\n<br>\r\n-Price strategy\r\n<br>\r\n-Upsell strategy\r\n<br>\r\n-Bonus strategy\r\n<br></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Create the title of your performance -\r\nWhen you have finished all the research\r\ndata, go to making a performance. It is\r\nclear that here is the creation of your f|rst\r\nstep.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Below are the steps you need to follow\r\nin order to optimize the title of your\r\nperformance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Use your gig title based on your\r\nresearch data model, use intriguing\r\nwords in the title to ensure that your\r\ntarget customers receive attention and\r\nare relevant to them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For e.g. If you offer a logo-designing\r\nperformance. Consider using titles such\r\nas</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I design 3 BEAUTIFUL logos in 24 hours</p>\r\n<p>I design a PROFESSIONAL logo with free</p>\r\n<p>I design 2 STUNNING logos BONUS Free\r\neditable file</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-All the above titles have been made\r\nbeautiful because they contain two\r\nimportant things.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>First, they all have intriguing words such\r\nas MAGNIFICENT, PROFESSIONAL,\r\nSTUNNING and BONUS. These words\r\ncertainly help to attract the attention of\r\nthe right people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Second, they all appeal to the most\r\nimportant aspects where every person\r\nwho wants to design a logo looks at.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For e.g. The first title \"3 BEAUTIFUL logos\r\nwithin 24 hours\" will appeal to the people\r\nwho need a logo urgently.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The second title \"PROFESSIONAL logos\r\nwith free revisions\" will appeal to the kind\r\nof people who want the option to include\r\ntheir changes in the logo design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The third title \"2 STUNNING logos BONUS\r\nFree editable file\" will appeal to people\r\nwho have some knowledge of the design\r\nof logos and want to customize the logo\r\naccording to their own wishes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Create the image of your performance</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-During your first homework you must\r\nhave noticed that some performances\r\nhave better images than others, which\r\nmakes them stand out.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Make a list of such images and get\r\ninspiration while modeling your image.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you are done with the original idea,\r\nuse free online tools for image editing,\r\nsuch as Pixlr or BeFunky to create the\r\nimage of your performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Write the description of the performance</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-The description of your performance\r\nplays an important role in convincing\r\nyour potential customers to place an\r\norder with you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You must therefore ensure that the\r\ndescription of your performance is\r\naccurate, clear and attractive to your\r\npotential customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Study descriptions of other top-related\r\ncomments to gain inspiration and model\r\nyour description.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do not forget that you never copy the\r\ndescription of another gig that prohibits\r\nit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Use theirs to get ideas for making your\r\nunique description.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also make sure that you store your\r\nperformance in the correct category to\r\nmaintain relevance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Use correct tags - Tags play the\r\nmost important role in ranking your\r\nperformance higher.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most people do not realize their\r\nimportance and ignore them therefore it\r\noffers you the best opportunity to catch\r\nup if you optimize your performance in\r\nthe right way with the help of accurate tags.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-In addition to all the points mentioned\r\nabove, you must ensure that your work is\r\ncredible and unique on Fiverr.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There may be many logo designers\r\nat Fiverr, but if you are the one who\r\nunderstands the needs of your customers\r\nand delivers the work in the best possible\r\nway, you can secure them as a customer\r\nfor a long time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Generating revenue:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Generating income is very simple. More\r\npeople place orders with you, more\r\nmoney you earn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your delivery activities affect your user\r\nratings that directly affect your placement\r\nof your order.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The simple rule of thumb is that the\r\nhigher the user ratings, the higher your\r\norders will be.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fiverr processes all your transactions\r\nsecurely, so you do not have to worry\r\nabout problems with the processing of\r\npayments.</p>\r\n\r\n', 'keywords for fiverr', '', '1', '1', 'description for fiverr', ''),
(21, '63', 'Resell Items on eBay', '14/07/2020', '', 'ebay.jpg', '<p>What is eBay.com?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>eBay is the most popular website for\r\nbuying and selling goods on the internet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is a place where individuals and\r\nbusinesses can buy or sell new or\r\nsecond-hand items, from books and\r\nclothing to cars and almost everything.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>This is how eBay works:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A seller mentions an item on eBay,\r\nalmost everything from antiques to\r\nmobile phones, books and sporting\r\ngoods.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The seller chooses to sell the item at a\r\nfixed price or only accept bids (auction\r\ntype offer).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In an auction type bid, bidding opens for\r\na price that the seller gives and stays on\r\neBay for a certain number of days.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Buyers then place bids on the item. When\r\nthe offer ends, the buyer wins with the\r\nhighest bid.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the Case of a fixed price indication, the\r\nfirst buyer who is willing to pay the selling\r\nprice receives the item.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Suitable for:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>People who are self-motivated and know\r\nhow to spread the word -to friends,\r\nrelatives, acquaintances and strangers\r\nusing online or offline media.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Required skills:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some experience with selling goods\r\nonline or offline is welcome, along with a\r\nsensible attitude.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Time needed to start selling on eBay:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To begin selling, you must first have an\r\neBay account and a PayPal account.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After this you have to register your\r\nproduct for which you have to upload\r\nsome product images and write an\r\nappealing description.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even if you are a beginner, you can\r\ncomplete all of the above tasks within a day or two.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Tips:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-If you are completely new to eBay and\r\nyour account has no feedback, it is a\r\ngood practice to get feedback before you\r\nstart selling something.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>People are very wary of buying\r\nsomething online nowadays, so if your\r\naccount has 0 feedback, nobody will buy\r\nfrom you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is recommended that you get at least\r\n10-15 feedback before selling anything.\r\nThe easiest way to get feedback is to buy\r\n10-15 S 0.99 items with free shipping.\r\nMany sellers leave you positive feedback\r\nin the right way when you pay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Start small - Most of eBay\'s resellers buy\r\na bulk wholesale inventory of a particular\r\nproduct and then sell it on eBay at a retail\r\nprice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you do not have money to buy a\r\nwholesaler, look for unwanted items in\r\nyour house that are in good condition and\r\nmake a list of them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Research - Now that you have a list\r\nwith a few ready to sell items, you must\r\nensure that there is a market for them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Take 10 minutes to show Google your\r\nitem and discover the real market value\r\non eBay and a number of e-commerce\r\nsites.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This will help you sell the right items\r\nmore competitively because you have the\r\nknowledge of your item\'s market and its\r\npricing strategies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also search for relevant targeted\r\nkeywords that help people flnd your items\r\nthrough the Google search engine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Create the title - Title is the most\r\nimportant factor to attract the attention\r\nof your potential buyer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Make sure that your title is attractive and\r\ncomplete and that you have included\r\ntargeted keywords.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You do not have to be a tech wizard for\r\nthis. Ask yourself the following question:\r\nwhat would a potential buyer of this item\r\ntype place in the search box?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Write description of the item - Fill in all\r\nthe fields in your list and ensure that\r\nyour textual description contains all the\r\ninformation that your potential buyer\r\ncould search for.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most lazy sellers ignore this and fail\r\nbadly at selling something on eBay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Upload photos of the item - Only upload\r\nhigh-quality photos. Make sure the\r\nphotos of the item are new, clear (not\r\nblurry) and cover the product from all\r\nangles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do not limit yourself to 2-3 photos upload\r\nat least 6 photos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Timing - Most expert sellers use a\r\n10-day offer that starts on Thursday, you\r\nshould also use it, it will give you two full\r\nweekends of eyeballs. Normally you will\r\nreceive the most traffic on weekends.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Generating revenue:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Generating income is very simple. More\r\npeople place orders with you, more\r\nmoney you earn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The quality and delivery of your item will\r\naffect your user feedback that directly\r\ninfluences your placement of the order.\r\nSo make sure that you deliver good\r\nquality articles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>eBay handles all your transactions\r\nsecurely, so you do not have to\r\nworry about problems with payment\r\nprocessing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As soon as you make a profit, you buy\r\nyour most sold products in bulk at a\r\nwholesale price and then sell them on the\r\nbasis of the retail price to increase your profits.</p>\r\n\r\n', 'keywords for ebay', '', '1', '1', 'Description for ebay', '');

